text:
Yo techkriti udghosh boi. Wing me sabse enthu wala launda tu hi hai. Placement season me support ke liye thanks bhai. Pehle pubg and now valorant, covid has made our friendship stronger.
Aise hi chaapte rho
author: Arpit Kumar Jhunjhunwala

text: Tere bina to MTH graduate hi nhi kar pata bhai. Remember jab hum first year se hi apne future ke liye kitna faltu ka discussion karte the. Ab to tujhe prof ke under project bhi mil gya and internship bhi lag gyi, ab placement me bhi chaap dena ganda wala
author: Arpit Kumar Jhunjhunwala

text: Yo civil ke bakchod launde, first year ka winter camp yad haai na kya hi bakchodi ki humne. Mujhe seconder banaya tha apna senate ke election me ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚. I will miss your political lectures and hope to meet u again.

text: Bro thank you for all the help in CS315 and during the internship season. Cisco me ja kar bhi aise hi chaapte rhna.
author: Arpit Kumar Jhunjhunwala

text: Yo gamer boi, you are of the most chill guy I met in IITK. Yaad hai jab exams ke bich me overwatch one week ke liye free hua tha. You introduced me to pubg and so many other games. First year me winter camp me kya hi bakchodi ki humne. Raat me sari lights off kar ke Resident evil khelna was one hell of an experience. I hope we meet again and relive those moments.
author: Arpit Kumar Jhunjhunwala

text: From the same batch in Vibrant to the same college we have come a long way. Campus me utna interact to nhi kar pae but I hope jaldi hi milte hai phir se. Placement me jaise chaapa waise hi aage bhi chaapte rhna ğŸ™ğŸ™
